# ChainMind — AI explorer for Robinhood Chain.
# Copy to `.env.local`; never commit real values.

# --- Groq (LLM) — REQUIRED to answer questions. https://console.groq.com/ ---
GROQ_API_KEY=
# Optional model override (default: llama-3.3-70b-versatile). A smaller model
# such as llama-3.1-8b-instant uses fewer tokens per day on the free tier.
# GROQ_MODEL=

# --- Robinhood Chain (EVM L2) ---
# Network selector: mainnet (chain 4663) | testnet (chain 46630). Default: mainnet.
# ROBINHOOD_NETWORK=mainnet
# Optional dedicated RPC (QuickNode / Chainstack / Alchemy) for higher rate
# limits. Falls back to the public RPC when unset.
# ROBINHOOD_RPC_URL=

# --- Blockscout (indexer / explorer) ---
# Override the indexer host or add a Pro key to raise rate limits. Defaults to
# the public Robinhood Chain Blockscout instance.
# BLOCKSCOUT_API_URL=https://robinhoodchain.blockscout.com/api
# BLOCKSCOUT_API_KEY=

# Stable origin for self-calls / metadata (optional; recommended on Vercel).
# NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://your-domain.vercel.app
